      <title>软银支持的电动滑板车初创公司寻求在印度进行 7.34 亿美元的 IPO</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/softbank-backed-e-scooter-startup-seeks-734-million-india-ipo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度最大的电动滑板车制造商 Ola Electric Mobility Ltd. 正在寻求通过首次公开募股筹集高达 614.6 亿卢比（7.34 亿美元）的资金，这将在日益普及的电动滑板车市场中考验投资者对这家电动汽车制造商的兴趣。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/softbank-backed-e-scooter-startup-seeks-734-million-india-ipo</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 05:11:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普发表支持加密货币的演讲后，比特币价格逼近 70,000 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/bitcoin-btc-hits-six-week-high-in-wake-of-trump-s-pro-crypto-speech</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普扩大其支持加密货币的议程以及美联储降息预期提振投资者情绪后，比特币触及了自 6 月中旬以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/bitcoin-btc-hits-six-week-high-in-wake-of-trump-s-pro-crypto-speech</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 04:09:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
